<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Crawler Challenge - Web Scraping CTF</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29 0%, #302b63 50%, #24243e 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 60px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea, #764ba2, #f5af19);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: gradient 3s ease infinite;
      background-size: 200% auto;
    }
    @keyframes gradient {
      0% { background-position: 0% center; }
      50% { background-position: 100% center; }
      100% { background-position: 0% center; }
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.3em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
    }
    .timer-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .levels-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .level-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: block;
    }
    .level-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
    }
    .level-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .level-number {
      font-size: 2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .level-points {
      background: rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.2);
      color: #2ecc71;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .level-title {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .level-desc {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 0.95em;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .level-tags {
      margin-top: 15px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .tag {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 0.8em;
    }
    .info-section {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .info-section h2 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #667eea;
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .info-item {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .info-item h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }
    .info-item p, .info-item ul {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 0.95em;
    }
    .info-item ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .info-item li {
      padding: 5px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .info-item li::before {
      content: '‚úì';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #2ecc71;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 40px 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .api-docs {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .api-docs h3 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .api-endpoint {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
    .method {
      color: #2ecc71;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>üï∑Ô∏è Crawler Challenge</h1>
    <p>Test your web scraping skills against progressively harder challenges.
       Use AI coding assistants, reverse engineer APIs, and bypass anti-bot measures!</p>
    <div class="timer-box" id="timer">
      ‚è±Ô∏è 60:00
