          Requires headless browser stealth!
        </p>
        <div class="level-tags">
          <span class="tag">Playwright</span>
          <span class="tag">Fingerprint</span>
          <span class="tag">Captcha</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/scoreboard" class="btn btn-primary">üèÜ Live Scoreboard</a>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <h2>üìã Rules & Information</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>‚è±Ô∏è Time Limit</h3>
          <p>60 minutes to complete all 4 levels. Rankings are based on total score and completion time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>üîß Allowed Tools</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Claude Code / Cursor / Copilot</li>
            <li>Web search engines</li>
            <li>Any programming language</li>
            <li>Browser DevTools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Submission Limits</h3>
          <p>Maximum 5 submissions per level. Only your highest score counts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <h3>üéØ Scoring</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Data completeness (30%)</li>
            <li>Data accuracy (40%)</li>
            <li>Honeypot avoidance (20%)</li>
            <li>Speed bonus (10%)</li>
          </ul>
