  ]
}</pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <h2>üîê Test Accounts (Level 3)</h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">
        Username: <code style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">team01</code> to <code style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">team20</code><br>
        Password: <code style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">test123</code>
